Anyone who wants to mod this game, please do.

Fixed bugs. See CHANGE LOG for details.
This is the last non-patch version. now thee number after the 1.x is a patch number.
This was a fun project, but I ran out of gas (ideas), and it was geting boring.

Controls. 

Arrow keys:move
Z:place
X:remove
C:Change direction(You point in the direction you move)
V: change block type.

How to use the lancher:

Type in the name of the world that you whant to play, and press enter.
You can also type "LAST" to play your last played world.

Moding:

Use this program:
https://github.com/python-nerd1235/2d-Mincraft-moder

HAVE FUN!   
